<h1>Create a template!</h1>
<h3>How to contribute:</h3>
<p>Write a story with exactly 10 fill in the blank spaces. Mark your blank space with a single underscore. This is very important. 😁</p>

<p>In the corresponding numbered inputs below the text area, enter the part of speech for each word. For example, if your first '_' is a noun, write "noun" in text input '1'.</p>

<p>When you're done with your story, hit submit!</p>

<form id="create-form" action="/libs" method="POST">
  <input type="text" placeholder="title" name="title" />
  <input type="text" placeholder="author" name="author" />
  <textarea id="create-text"></textarea>
  <input type="text" placeholder="1" name="label_1" />
  <input type="text" placeholder="2" name="label_2" />
  <input type="text" placeholder="3" name="label_3" />
  <input type="text" placeholder="4" name="label_4" />
  <input type="text" placeholder="5" name="label_5" />
  <input type="text" placeholder="6" name="label_6" />
  <input type="text" placeholder="7" name="label_7" />
  <input type="text" placeholder="8" name="label_8" />
  <input type="text" placeholder="9" name="label_9" />
  <input type="text" placeholder="10" name="label_10" />
  <input type="submit" />
</form>

